9-10-07|format=|publisher=立場新聞|language=|archive-date=2021-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210708055329/https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/10-6-%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E7%AA%81%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E8%A1%9D%E6%92%9E%E9%80%94%E4%BA%BA-%E7%9A%84%E7%B8%BD-%E9%81%87%E8%B7%AF%E9%9A%9C%E5%A4%B1%E6%8E%A7-%E6%B7%B1%E5%88%87%E6%85%B0%E5%95%8F%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[守護香港大聯盟|守護香港大聯盟]]發起籌款，向鄭姓司機捐贈52萬，他亦拒絕向受傷女生道歉，稱自己毋須負上責任。<ref>{{cite news |title=被毆的士司機傷勢嚴重 家人遭暴徒「死亡威脅」 |url=http://www.takungpao.com.hk/hongkong/text/2019/1009/359336.html |work=文匯報 |date=2019-10-09 |accessdate=2019-10-09 |archive-date=2019-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191009030443/http://www.takungpao.com.hk/hongkong/text/2019/1009/359336.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

